title: I wont work
body: This thing keeps popping up I restarted my computer and everything. This is the first time this has happen to me and is there a way to fix this. I just want to play some league with the bros :(.

replies.body: I just uninstalled it completely and reinstalled it xD

There are a few things that can cause patching issues such as this. Check out our [Patching Issues guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434-Patching-Issues) for a consolidated list of steps that are most likely to resolve this.

Let me know if those steps helped.

Nothing is working i tried the Hextech Repair tool and I also clicked the "?" on the launcher and hit repair and it still didn't do anything im just  gonna re-download the client and see if that works
At what percentage (%) during patching are you failing at?
PARRYSUPER from Riot helped me out a lot and now my problem is fixed hope this never happens again but if it does I might know what to do. Love you man/woman
